<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-1896] Support MMType1 (Multiple Master) Fonts</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1896</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;MMType1 Fonts are not supported. They are described on p.416 of the 1.7 spec. I attach a sample file.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
